These benchmarks for GLIMMER are written by Magnus Hagdorn. They are based on 
the benchmarks proposed by Bueler et al 2005.

E. Bueler, C. S. Lingle, J. A. Kallen-Brown, D. N. Covey, L. N. Bowman 
(2005) "Exact solutions and numerical verification for isothermal ice sheets,"
J. Glaciol. 51 (no. 173), 291--306.
